<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Appointment Letter</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 40px;
            background: white;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            border-bottom: 3px solid {{#if brandKit.colors.[0]}}{{brandKit.colors.[0]}}{{else}}#1e40af{{/if}};
            padding-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .company-name {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: {{#if brandKit.colors.[0]}}{{brandKit.colors.[0]}}{{else}}#1e40af{{/if}};
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        .company-address {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .document-title {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            margin: 30px 0;
            text-align: center;
            color: #333;
        }
        .date-ref {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .content {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            text-align: justify;
        }
        .content p {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .details-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin: 20px 0;
            background: #f9f9f9;
        }
        .details-table th,
        .details-table td {
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            padding: 12px;
            text-align: left;
        }
        .details-table th {
            background-color: {{#if brandKit.colors.[0]}}{{brandKit.colors.[0]}}{{else}}#1e40af{{/if}};
            color: white;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .signature-section {
            margin-top: 50px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }
        .signature-box {
            text-align: center;
            width: 200px;
        }
        .signature-line {
            border-top: 1px solid #333;
            margin-top: 60px;
            padding-top: 5px;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 40px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
            padding-top: 20px;
        }
        .highlight {
            background-color: #fff3cd;
            padding: 15px;
            border-left: 4px solid {{#if brandKit.colors.[0]}}{{brandKit.colors.[0]}}{{else}}#1e40af{{/if}};
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <div class="company-name">{{companyName}}</div>
        <div class="company-address">{{companyAddress}}</div>
        {{#if companyPhone}}<div>Phone: {{companyPhone}} | Email: {{companyEmail}}</div>{{/if}}
    </div>

    <div class="document-title">Appointment Letter</div>

    <div class="date-ref">
        <div><strong>Date:</strong> {{appointmentDate}}</div>
        <div><strong>Ref:</strong> {{refNumber}}</div>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
        <p><strong>{{employeeName}}</strong><br>
        {{#if employeeAddress}}{{employeeAddress}}{{/if}}</p>

        <p><strong>Subject: Appointment as {{position}}</strong></p>

        <p>Dear {{employeeName}},</p>

        <p>We are pleased to inform you that you have been appointed as <strong>{{position}}</strong> in the <strong>{{department}}</strong> department of {{companyName}}, effective from <strong>{{startDate}}</strong>.</p>

        <p>Your appointment is subject to the terms and conditions mentioned below and as per the company policies:</p>

        <div class="details-table">
            <table class="details-table">
                <tr>
                    <th>Particulars</th>
                    <th>Details</th>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><strong>Employee Name</strong></td>
                    <td>{{employeeName}}</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><strong>Position</strong></td>
                    <td>{{position}}</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><strong>Department</strong></td>
                    <td>{{department}}</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><strong>Date of Appointment</strong></td>
                    <td>{{appointmentDate}}</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><strong>Reporting Manager</strong></td>
                    <td>{{reportingTo}}</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><strong>Work Location</strong></td>
                    <td>{{workLocation}}</td>
                </tr>
                {{#if probationPeriod}}
                <tr>
                    <td><strong>Probation Period</strong></td>
                    <td>{{probationPeriod}}</td>
                </tr>
                {{/if}}
            </table>
        </div>

        <div class="highlight">
            <p><strong>Terms and Conditions:</strong></p>
            <ul>
                <li>You will be governed by the rules, regulations, and policies of the company as amended from time to time.</li>
                <li>You are required to maintain confidentiality of all company information and data.</li>
                <li>Your employment is subject to satisfactory completion of probation period{{#if probationPeriod}} of {{probationPeriod}}{{/if}}.</li>
                <li>You will be required to give {{#if noticePeriod}}{{noticePeriod}}{{else}}30 days{{/if}} notice in writing before leaving the organization.</li>
                <li>The company reserves the right to terminate your services with appropriate notice as per company policy.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <p>We welcome you to our organization and look forward to a long and mutually beneficial association.</p>

        <p>Please confirm your acceptance of this appointment by signing and returning a copy of this letter.</p>

        <p>Congratulations and welcome to {{companyName}}!</p>
    </div>

    <div class="signature-section">
        <div class="signature-box">
            <div class="signature-line">
                <strong>For {{companyName}}</strong><br>
                Authorized Signatory<br>
                HR Department
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="signature-box">
            <div class="signature-line">
                <strong>Employee Acceptance</strong><br>
                {{employeeName}}<br>
                Date: ___________
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        <p>This is a computer-generated document and does not require a physical signature.</p>
        <p>Generated on {{currentDate}} | {{companyName}} - Professional Document System</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>